# Title: Use of Wfc.exe
# Author: Christopher Peacock @SecurePeacock, SCYTHE @scythe_io
# Date: 2022-06-01
# Level: medium
# Description: The Workflow Command-line Compiler can be used for AWL bypass and is listed in Microsoft's recommended block rules.
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1127
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_lolbin_wfc.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate use by a software developer

Image="*\\wfc.exe" OR OriginalFileName="wfc.exe"